theorem dense_iff_interior_closure_eq_univ {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    Dense A ↔ interior (closure A) = (Set.univ : Set X) := by
  classical
  constructor
  · intro hDense
    simpa using
      (interior_closure_eq_univ_of_dense (X := X) (A := A) hDense)
  · intro hIntEq
    have h_subset : (Set.univ : Set X) ⊆ closure A := by
      have h_int_sub : interior (closure A) ⊆ closure A := interior_subset
      simpa [hIntEq] using h_int_sub
    have h_closure_eq : (closure A : Set X) = (Set.univ : Set X) := by
      apply Set.Subset.antisymm
      · intro _ _; trivial
      · exact h_subset
    simpa [Dense] using h_closure_eq

theorem interior_subset_closure {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    interior A ⊆ closure A := by
  intro x hx
  have hxA : x ∈ A := interior_subset hx
  exact subset_closure hxA
